ALGORITHM

1.	Start
2.	Initialize DPTR to 4700H
3.	Read the number from memory location 4700H and store it in B register
4.	Increment DPTR and read the value from next memory location and store it to accumulator
5.	Multiply the value of B register and accumulator and store the result to the accumulator
6.	Increment DPTR and store the value of Accumulator to memory location 4702H
7.	Increment DPTR and store the value of B register to memory location 4703H
8.	Stop

